d the idea is being rejected by the government. \par \par \uc2  "So, it is probable that they are happy to see our \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  become unstable." \par \par \uc2  Former Finance Minister Fuad Bawazier said that the idea to apply the currency board system (CBS) had been rejected in the past. \par \par \uc2  "I proposed CBS to Soeharto, and he almost agreed. But the plan fell through because he did not agree to certain parts of CBS." \par \par \uc2  He added that the idea is relevant amidst the current weak rupiah. \par \par \uc2  "If the system had been applied in the past, we probably would have emerged from the crisis by now." (yn/ens/mt). \par \par \uc2 Document bisnis0020010804dw7a000cp\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
