\par \par \uc2  Furthermore, his acts had led the country to  bankruptcy, new styles of \par \par \uc2  corruption, collusion and nepotism, and national disintegration, the statement \par \par \uc2  said. \par \par \uc2  The students' consortium also expressed concern that if President \par \par \uc2  Abdurrahman Wahid remained in office, the country might face worse conditions in \par \par \uc2  the future. \par \par \uc2  On Tuesday, Rais said that the MPR annual session on August will not be \par \par \uc2  changed into a special session, moreover to topple Gus Dur. \par \par \uc2  However, if Gus Dur in the next three months after the August annual \par \par \uc2  session, failed to improve his performance and restore the country's \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2 , he \par \par \uc2  would have to return his mandate to the people. \par \par \uc2  "It is up to the people. But clearly, at the next annual session, I as MPR \par \par \uc2  speaker can only do what is required under the democratic process and the wish of the 700 members of Assembly," Rais said. \par \par \uc2 Document antara0020010804dw7r005dp\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw139\pich40\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal2085\pichgoal600
