re. \par \par \uc2  "The US has asked (the Indonesian government) to hand over the list soon, \par \par \uc2  along with its estimated value in US dollars," he said. \par \par \uc2  President Wahid's meeting with Harkins was originally scheduled to be held \par \par \uc2  in Washington DC, but Harkins and former US ambassador to Indonesia, Paul \par \par \uc2  Wolfowitz, visited him in Baltimore, cutting his US trip by 14 hours. \par \par \uc2  The president was supposed to arrive here Tuesday had the meeting with \par \par \uc2  Harkins been held in Washington DC. \par \par \uc2  Atambua incident \par \par \uc2  Commenting on the Atambua killings, President Wahid expressed his deep \par \par \uc2  concern over the incident. \par \par \uc2  He also expressed hope that the international community would hasten to \par \par \uc2  fulfill its promise to provide funds to repatriate or relocate the remaining \par \par \uc2  East Timorese refugees in Indonesia. \par \par \uc2  A mob of East Timorese refugees, angered by the murder of a former pro- \par \par \uc2  integration fighter, attacked and burned the office of the UN High Commissioner for Refugees (UNHCR) in the town of Atambua in East Nusa Tenggara province last Wednesday. \par \par \uc2  Three UNHCR workers -- a Croatian, a Puerto Rican and an Ethiopian -- were \par \par \uc2  killed. \par \par \uc2  President Wahid reiterated that Indonesia does not want to be blamed for the \par \par \uc2  clashes among East Timorese. \par \par \uc2  He said many of them are reluctant to return to East Timor due to the \par \par \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  and security \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainties\b0 \highlight\uc2  in the newly independent territory. \par \par \uc2  He also noted that the funds being used to support the refugees in East Nusa \par \par \uc2  Tenggara come from the province's \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  for development. \par \par \uc2  Asked whether the incident would affect the meeting of donor countries \par \par \uc2  grouped in the Consultative Group on Indonesia (CGI) in Tokyo this October, the \par \par \uc2  president expressed hope that it would not. \par \par \uc2  "We hope that there would be an improvement (in the situation in Atambua) \par \par \uc2  before the CGI meeting," he said. \par \par \uc2  Iraq visit \par \par \uc2  President Wahid also reaffirmed his plan to visit Baghdad second week of \par \par \uc2  November to meet with his Iraqi counterpart Saddam Hussein, despite objections \par \par \uc2  from the US. \par \par \uc2  The US in the early 1990s imposed an embargo on Iraq after the latter \par \par \uc2  attacked Kuwait. \par \par \uc2  "How could we talk if a meeting is not allowed to take place?" he asked. \par \par \uc2  He noted that one of the points to be discussed in his meeting with Saddam \par \par \uc2  is the possibility of releasing some 600 Kuwaitis still detained in Iraq. \par \par \uc2  "We should not let the Iraqis become the victims," he said about the US \par \par \uc2  embargo which has led to the death of hundreds of Iraqis due to the deprivation of food and medicine. \par \par \uc2 Document antara0020010804dw9b0020f\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
