 of four dissolved offices of state ministers - the office of the state minister of \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  works; the office of the state minister of cooperatives, small and medium enterprises; the office of the state minister of transmigration and population; and the office of the state minister of tourism and arts. \par \par \uc2  "We want to settle the placements as soon as we can but we all know the city has just recovered from the \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  crisis and we have many other priorities, so just have to be very selective about this," Kahfi said. \par \par \uc2  He added that numerous government employees still had not found jobs following the closure of the agency for the propagation of Pancasila in 1998. \par \par \uc2  "We have established a working team consisting of city secretary officials, the city administration office and other working units from this office. \par \par \uc2  "They have been working since last month to resolve the problems," Kahfi said. (dja) \par \par \uc2  Copyright 2000 The Jakarta Post. \par \par \uc2 Document jkpost0020010812dw9u003xb\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
